# Documentation Location

All project documentation (`.md` files) must be created in the `docs/` folder.

- **Correct:** `docs/DEPLOY.md`, `docs/README.md`, `docs/API.md`
- **Incorrect:** `DEPLOY.md`, `API.md` at project root
- **Exception:** `README.md` at project root is allowed for GitHub repo display

When creating or moving documentation, use the `docs/` directory.
